---
alwaysApply: true
---
- All project dependencies must be declared in requirements.txt
- Standard dependencies must include:
    - fastapi
    - uvicorn[standard]
    - pytest
    - pytest-cov 
    - httpx
    - python-dotenv
- Future DB dependencies must be grouped under a commented section called # databases (future).
- Any modification to dependencies must trigger:
    - README update
    - Dockerfile update
    - CI pipeline validation
